Welcome To The Boyar Value Group


The Boyar Value Groups’ mission is to search for value on behalf of our clients.
Since 1975 the Boyar family of companies has focused on creating value for our clients — by seeking out and investing in companies whose intrinsic value significantly exceeds that of its current market price. We are committed to the idea that through hard work, patience and dedication to the core tenets of value investing, it is possible to buy a dollar for fifty cents. While many fads and gimmicks have come and gone since we started in the investment business, we’ve remained steadfast in our belief that value investing is the best way to preserve and create wealth in the long term.
These core values not only form our philosophy, but lie at the heart of what we do both in our money management and institutional research divisions. We look forward to putting our knowledge and expertise to work for you.  



Boyar Asset Management


Boyar Research




We have been managing money since 1983 utilizing our proprietary in-house value oriented equity strategy. We manage money for high net worth individuals and institutions via separately managed accounts. In addition, since 1998 we have managed the Boyar Value Fund to serve individuals who cannot meet our minimum investment criteria for separately managed accounts.
Visit Boyar Asset Management >>


Since 1975 we have been producing independent research on intrinsically undervalued companies across the market capitalization spectrum and in a wide variety of industries using a business person’s approach to stock market investing. It is interesting to note that since 1975, approximately 40% of all the companies that have appeared in our flagship publication Asset Analysis Focus have been take over or profitably liquidated*.
Visit Boyar Research >>



*Past performance is no guarantee of future results.








