About the Team


As of September 2012, The Boyar Value Group has a team of 6 analysts/investment professionals with approximately 16 years of investment experience on average. The team has a diverse background consisting of CFA charterholders, M.B.A.’s, and J.D.s. The team collectively has analyzed thousands of companies in a variety of industries throughout their respective careers. Being able to not only accurately analyze a business but also having the ability to put that analysis within a historical frame work is critically important in terms of separating businesses selling at a discount to intrinsic value from value traps.








