REDEMPTION FEES

The Fund may assess a short-term redemption fee of 2.00% of the total redemption amount if a shareholder sells their shares after holding them for less than 60 days. The redemption fee is paid directly to the Fund.  For year ended December 31, 2007, the Fund assessed $2,027 in redemption fees. This fee does not apply to shares acquired through reinvestment of dividends and other distributions.
